&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;***Please note this is an INTERNAL VACANCY ONLY for NUH employees, therefore only current employees of Nottingham University Hospitals NHS Trust will be considered for the post.***&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity for a years secondment , to join the Department of Clinical Haematology as part of the AOS team has arisen. The team work closely with their medical colleagues, and the wards within the CAS directorate. As part of this team you will be expected to review patients either with or on behalf of the medical team. You will need to have substantial haematology knowledge, be able to work on your own, and posses excellent communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
